short.en: You can set your bookmark directory as a tab

long.en:
We provide a way to provide a navigation website as a tab startup page by specifying a local bookmark directory, while providing some elegant wallpapers and a certain degree of customization capabilities.

If you encounter problems during use, please don't worry, bad reviews can't solve the problem. You can give feedback on the link below, and I will follow up in time.
